## <a name="france-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4464">Номер водительского удостоверения для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4464">France driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4465">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4465">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4466">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4466">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4467">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4467">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4468">12 цифр с проверкой подлинности, чтобы избежать путаницы с похожими шаблонами, например французскими номерами телефонов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4468">12 digits with validation to discount similar patterns such as French telephone numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4469">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4469">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4470">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4470">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4471">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4471">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4472">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4472">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4473">функция Func_french_drivers_license находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4473">the function Func_french_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4474">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_french_drivers_license.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4474">a keyword from Keyword_french_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="18e55a36-a01b-4b0f-943d-dc10282a1824" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_french_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="france-health-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4601">Номер медицинского страхования для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4601">France health insurance number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4602">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4602">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4603">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4603">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4604">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4604">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4605">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4605">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4606">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4606">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4607">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4607">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4608">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4608">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4609">21-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4609">21 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4610">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4610">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4611">21-значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4611">21 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4612">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4612">ten digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4613">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4613">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4614">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4614">ten digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4615">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4615">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4616">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4616">a digit</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4617">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4617">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4618">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4618">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4619">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4619">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4620">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4620">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4621">Regex Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4621">the regex Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4622">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4622">a keyword from Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Health Insurance Number -->
      <Entity id="9bc2069e-76df-4ff9-ac02-2f519469e236" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4623">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4623">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_france_health_insurance_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4624">Keyword_France_health_insurance_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4624">Keyword_France_health_insurance_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4625">страховая карта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4625">insurance card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4626">carte vitale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4626">carte vitale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4627">carte d'assuré social</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4627">carte d'assuré social</span></span>


## <a name="france-national-id-card-cni"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4628">Национальный удостоверение личности для Франции (CNI)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4628">France national id card (CNI)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4629">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4629">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4630">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4630">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4631">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4631">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4632">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4632">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4633">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4633">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4634">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4634">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4635">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4635">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4636">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4636">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4637">регулярное выражение Regex_france_cni находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4637">The regular expression Regex_france_cni finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4638">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4638">A keyword from Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France CNI -->
    <Entity id="f741ac74-1bc0-4665-b69b-f0c7f927c0c4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="65">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_france_cni" />
        <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4639">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4639">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4645">cni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4645">cni</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4646">compte bancaire</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4646">compte bancaire</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4647">national identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4647">national identification number</span></span>

## <a name="france-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4652">Номер паспорта гражданина Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4652">France passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4653">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4653">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4654">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4654">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4655">девять цифр и букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4655">nine digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4656">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4656">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4657">девять цифр и букв:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4657">nine digits and letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4658">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4658">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4659">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4659">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4660">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4660">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4661">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4661">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4662">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4662">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4663">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4663">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4664">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4664">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4665">функция Func_fr_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4665">The function Func_fr_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4666">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4666">A keyword from Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- France Passport Number -->
<Entity id="3008b884-8c8c-4cd8-a289-99f34fc7ff5d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_fr_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="france-social-security-number-insee-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4687">Номер социального обеспечения для Франции (INSEE) или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4687">France social security number (INSEE) or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4688">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации номера социального обеспечения ЕС и эквивалентного ИД и доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4688">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Social Security Number and Equivalent ID sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4689">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4689">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4690">15 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4690">15 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4691">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4691">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4692">Должен соответствовать одному из двух шаблонов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4692">Must match one of two patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4693">13 цифр, за которыми следуют пробелы, за которыми следуют две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4693">13 digits followed by a space followed by two digits</span></span><br/>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4694">или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4694">or</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4695">15 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4695">15 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4696">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4696">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4697">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4697">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4698">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4698">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4699">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 95 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4699">A DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4700">Функция Func_french_insee или Func_fr_insee находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4700">The function Func_french_insee or Func_fr_insee finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4701">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_fr_insee;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4701">A keyword from Keyword_fr_insee is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4702">контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4702">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4703">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4703">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4704">Функция Func_french_insee или Func_fr_insee находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4704">The function Func_french_insee or Func_fr_insee finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4705">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_fr_insee не находится;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4705">No keyword from Keyword_fr_insee is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4706">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4706">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- France INSEE -->
<Entity id="71f62b97-efe0-4aa1-aa49-e14de253619d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Match idRef="Func_fr_insee" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Match idRef="Func_fr_insee" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="france-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4732">Идентификационный номер налога для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4732">France tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4733">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4733">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4734">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4734">13 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4735">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4735">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4736">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4736">13 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4737">Одна цифра, которая должна быть 0, 1, 2 или 3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4737">One digit that must be 0, 1, 2, or 3</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4738">1 цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4738">1 digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4739">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4739">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4740">2 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4740">2 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4741">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4741">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4742">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4742">3 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4743">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4743">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4744">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4744">3 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4745">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4745">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4746">3 проверок цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4746">3 check digits</span></span> 

  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4747">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4747">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4748">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4748">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4749">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4749">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4750">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4750">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4751">Функция находит  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4751">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4752">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4752">A keyword from  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4753">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4753">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4754">Функция находит  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4754">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- France Tax Identification Number (numéro SPI.) -->
      <Entity id="ed59e77e-171d-442c-9ec1-88e2ebcb5b0a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

#### <a name="keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4756">Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4756">Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4760">налоговый идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4760">tax identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4761">tax no #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4761">tax no#</span></span>

## <a name="france-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4774">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4774">France value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4775">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4775">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4776">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4776">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4777">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4777">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4778">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4778">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4779">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4779">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4780">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4780">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4781">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4781">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4782">13 символов букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4782">13 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4783">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4783">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4784">13 символов букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4784">13 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4785">две буквы — FR (без чувствительность к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4785">two letters  - FR (case insensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4786">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4786">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4787">две буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4787">two letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4788">дополнительное пространство, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4788">an optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4789">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4789">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4790">дополнительное пространство, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4790">an optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4791">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4791">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4792">дополнительное пространство, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4792">an optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4793">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4793">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4794">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4794">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4795">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4795">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4796">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4796">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4797">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4797">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4798">Функция Func_france_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4798">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4799">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4799">A keyword from Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4800">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4800">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4801">Функция Func_france_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4801">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="949121e6-ad9f-4379-8731-710342baea78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4802">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4802">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4804">номер плательщика НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4804">vat number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4808">siren identification no numéro d'identification taxe sur valeur ajoutée</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4808">siren identification no numéro d'identification taxe sur valeur ajoutée</span></span>

## <a name="germany-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4814">Номер водительского удостоверения для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4814">Germany driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4815">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4815">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4816">сочетание 11 цифр и букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4816">combination of 11 digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4817">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4817">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4818">11 цифр и букв (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4818">11 digits and letters (not case sensitive):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4819">цифра или буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4819">a digit or letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4820">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4820">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4821">шесть цифр или букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4821">six digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4822">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4822">a digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4823">цифра или буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4823">a digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4824">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4824">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4825">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4825">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4826">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4826">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4827">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4827">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4828">Функция Func_german_drivers_license находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4828">The function Func_german_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4829">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_german_drivers_license_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4829">A keyword from Keyword_german_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4830">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4830">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- German Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="91da9335-1edb-45b7-a95f-5fe41a16c63c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_german_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4979">Номер удостоверения личности для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4979">Germany identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4980">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4980">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4981">с 1 ноября 2010 г.: девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4981">since 1 November 2010: Nine letters and digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4982">с 1 апреля 1987 г. по 31 октября 2010 г.: 10 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4982">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010: 10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4983">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4983">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4984">с 1 ноября 2010 г.:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4984">since 1 November 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4985">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4985">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4986">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4986">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4987">с 1 апреля 1987 г. по 31 октября 2010 г.:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4987">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4988">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4988">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4989">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4989">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4990">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4990">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4991">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4991">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4992">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4992">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4993">регулярное выражение Regex_germany_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4993">The regular expression Regex_germany_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4994">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_germany_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4994">A keyword from Keyword_germany_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Germany Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="e577372f-c42e-47a0-9d85-bebed1c237d4" recommendedConfidence="65" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_germany_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_germany_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_germany_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4996">Keyword_germany_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4996">Keyword_germany_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4997">ausweis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4997">ausweis</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4998">gpid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4998">gpid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-4999">identification</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-4999">identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5000">identifikation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5000">identifikation</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5001">identifizierungsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5001">identifizierungsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5002">identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5002">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5003">идентификациный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5003">identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5004">id-nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5004">id-nummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5005">личный ид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5005">personal id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5008">persönliche identifikationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5008">persönliche identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5009">persönliche-id-nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5009">persönliche-id-nummer</span></span>


## <a name="germany-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5010">Номер паспорта гражданина Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5010">Germany passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5011">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5011">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5012">десять цифр или букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5012">ten digits or letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5013">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5013">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5014">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5014">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5015">первый символ — это цифра или буква из этого набора (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5015">first character is a digit or a letter from this set (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5016">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5016">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5017">пять цифр или букв из этого набора (C, -H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5017">five digits or letters from this set (C, -H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5018">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5018">a digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5019">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5019">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5020">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5020">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5021">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5021">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5022">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5022">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5023">функция Func_german_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5023">The function Func_german_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5024">Ключевое слово `Keyword_german_passport` из или `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5024">A keyword from `Keyword_german_passport` or `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5025">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5025">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5026">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5026">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5027">функция Func_german_passport_data находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5027">The function Func_german_passport_data finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5028">Ключевое слово `Keyword_german_passport` из или `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5028">A keyword from `Keyword_german_passport` or `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5029">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5029">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- German Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="2e3da144-d42b-47ed-b123-fbf78604e52c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport_data" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5052">Идентификационный номер налога для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5052">Germany tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5053">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5053">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5054">11 цифр без пробелов и делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5054">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5055">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5055">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5056">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5056">11 digits :</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5057">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5057">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5058">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5058">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5059">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5059">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5060">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5060">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5061">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5061">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5062">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5062">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5063">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5063">Two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5064">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5064">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5065">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5065">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5066">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5066">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5067">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5067">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5068">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5068">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5069">Функция находит  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5069">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5070">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5070">A keyword from  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5071">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5071">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5072">Функция находит  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5072">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Germany Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="43316a89-9880-40cf-b980-04bc7eefcec5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5082">tax no #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5082">tax no#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5084">налоговый номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5084">tax number</span></span>

## <a name="germany-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5098">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость в Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5098">Germany value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5099">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5099">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5100">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5100">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5101">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5101">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5102">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5102">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5103">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5103">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5104">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5104">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5105">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5105">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5106">11 символов букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5106">11 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5107">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5107">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5108">11-символьный буквонумерный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5108">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5109">буква D или d</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5109">a letter D or d</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5110">буква E или e</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5110">a letter E or e</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5111">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5111">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5112">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5112">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5113">необязательный пробел или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5113">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5114">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5114">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5115">необязательный пробел или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5115">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5116">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5116">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5117">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5117">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5118">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5118">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5119">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5119">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5120">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5120">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5121">Функция Func_germany_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5121">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5122">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5122">A keyword from Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5123">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5123">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5124">Функция Func_germany_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5124">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Germany Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="db177eb2-8811-4842-bffc-128c14aa219f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="greece-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5134">Номер водительского удостоверения для Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5134">Greece driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5135">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5135">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5136">девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5136">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5137">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5137">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5138">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5138">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5139">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5139">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5140">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5140">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5141">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5141">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5142">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5142">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5143">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5143">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5144">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5144">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greece Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="7a2200b5-aacf-4e3c-ab36-136d3e68b7da" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="greece-national-id-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5270">Карточка национального удостоверения личности для Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5270">Greece national ID card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5271">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5271">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5272">Сочетание 7–8 букв и чисел, а также тире.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5272">Combination of 7-8 letters and numbers plus a dash</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5273">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5273">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5274">Семь букв и чисел (старый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5274">Seven letters and numbers (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5275">одна буква (любая буква греческого алфавита);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5275">One letter (any letter of the Greek alphabet)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5276">тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5276">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5277">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5277">Six digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5278">Восемь букв и чисел (новый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5278">Eight letters and numbers (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5279">две буквы, которые в прописном виде есть как в греческом, так и латинском алфавите (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5279">Two letters whose uppercase character occurs in both the Greek and Latin alphabets (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5280">тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5280">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5281">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5281">Six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5282">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5282">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5283">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5283">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5284">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5284">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5285">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5285">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5286">регулярное выражение Regex_greece_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5286">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5287">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_greece_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5287">A keyword from Keyword_greece_id_card is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5288">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5288">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5289">регулярное выражение Regex_greece_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5289">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Greece National ID Card -->
      <Entity id="82568215-1da1-46d3-874a-d2294d81b5ac" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5290">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5290">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_greece_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5291">Keyword_greece_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5291">Keyword_greece_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5292">греческий ид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5292">greek id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5293">греческий национальный ид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5293">greek national id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5294">личная карточка для греческих личных удостоверений</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5294">greek personal id card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5295">греческий ид полиции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5295">greek police id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5296">identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5296">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5297">tautotita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5297">tautotita</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5298">ταυτότητα</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5298">ταυτότητα</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5299">ταυτότητας</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5299">ταυτότητας</span></span>


## <a name="greece-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5300">Номер паспорта гражданина Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5300">Greece passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5301">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5301">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5302">Две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или седиметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5302">Two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5303">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5303">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5304">Две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5304">Two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5305">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5305">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5306">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5306">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5307">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5307">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5308">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5308">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5309">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5309">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5310">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5310">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5311">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_greece_eu_passport_date` ДД MMM YY (пример — 28 августа 19) или находится ключевое слово `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5311">The regular expression `Regex_greece_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM YY (Example - 28 Aug 19) or a keyword from `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5312">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5312">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5313">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5313">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5314">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5314">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greece Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7e65eb47-cdf9-4f52-8f90-2a27d5ee67e3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5315">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5315">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_greece_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5327">Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5327">Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5330">αριθμός διαβατηριο</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5330">αριθμός διαβατηριο</span></span>


## <a name="greece-social-security-number-amka"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5331">Номер социального обеспечения для Греция (AMKA)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5331">Greece Social Security Number (AMKA)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5332">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5332">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5333">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5333">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5334">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5334">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5335">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5335">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5336">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5336">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5337">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5337">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5338">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5338">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5339">Одиннадцати цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5339">Eleven digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5340">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5340">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5341">6 цифр в качестве даты рождения YYMMDD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5341">6 digits as date of birth YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5342">4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5342">4 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5343">проверяемая цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5343">a check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5344">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5344">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5345">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5345">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5346">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5346">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5347">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5347">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5348">Функция находит  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5348">The function  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5349">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5349">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5350">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5350">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5351">Функция находит  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5351">The function  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Greece Social Security Number (AMKA) -->
      <Entity id="e39b03f4-50ea-41ae-af7a-a4b9539596ad" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_greece_eu_ssn" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_greece_eu_ssn" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5352">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5352">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5353">Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5353">Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5354">ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5354">ssn</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5355">ssn #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5355">ssn#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5356">social security no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5356">social security no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5357">socialsecurityno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5357">socialsecurityno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5358">social security number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5358">social security number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5359">amka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5359">amka</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5360">a.m.k.a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5360">a.m.k.a.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5361">Αριθμού Μητρώου Κοινωνικής Ασφάλισης</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5361">Αριθμού Μητρώου Κοινωνικής Ασφάλισης</span></span>


## <a name="greece-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5362">Идентификационный номер налога для Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5362">Greece tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5363">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5363">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5364">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5364">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5365">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5365">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5366">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5366">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5367">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5367">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5368">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5368">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5369">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5369">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5370">Девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5370">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5371">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5371">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5372">Девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5372">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5373">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5373">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5374">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5374">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5375">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5375">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5376">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5376">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5377">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5377">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-5378">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-5378">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greek Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="15a54a5a-53d4-4080-ad43-a2a4fe1d3bf7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
