## <a name="ireland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6072">Номер паспорта гражданина Ирландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6072">Ireland passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6073">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6073">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6074">Две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6074">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6075">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6075">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6076">Две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6076">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6077">две цифры или буквы (без учета регистра);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6077">Two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6078">семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6078">Seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6079">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6079">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6080">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6080">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6081">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6081">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6082">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6082">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6083">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6083">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6084">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6084">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6085">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date` ДД MMM/MMM ГГ ГГ (пример — 01 BEA/MAY 1988) или находится ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6085">The regular expression `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 01 BEA/MAY 1988) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6086">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6086">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6087">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6087">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6088">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6088">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Ireland Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="a2130f27-9ee2-4103-84f9-a6b1ee7d0cbf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="ireland-personal-public-service-pps-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6112">Номер личной службы (PPS) для Ирландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6112">Ireland personal public service (PPS) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6113">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6113">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6114">Старый формат (до 31 декабря 2012 г.):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6114">Old format (until 31 Dec 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6115">семь цифр, за которыми следуют 1–2 буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6115">seven digits followed by 1-2 letters</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6116">Новый формат (1 января 2013 г. и после):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6116">New format (1 Jan 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6117">семь цифр, за которыми следуют две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6117">seven digits followed by two letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6118">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6118">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6119">Старый формат (до 31 декабря 2012 г.):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6119">Old format (until 31 Dec 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6120">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6120">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6121">от одной до двух букв (без чувствительность к буквам);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6121">one to two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6122">Новый формат (1 января 2013 г. и после):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6122">New format (1 Jan 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6123">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6123">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6124">буква (без чувствительность к букве), которая является алфавитной провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6124">a letter (not case sensitive) which is an alphabetic check digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6125">Необязательная буква в диапазоне A-I или W</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6125">An optional letter in the range A-I, or “W”</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6126">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6126">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6127">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6127">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6128">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6128">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6129">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6129">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6130">Функция Func_ireland_pps находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6130">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6131">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6131">A keyword from Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6132">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6132">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6133">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6133">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6134">функция Func_ireland_pps находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6134">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6135">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6135">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ireland Personal Public Service (PPS) Number -->
      <Entity id="1cdb674d-c19a-4fcf-9f4b-7f56cc87345a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85" relaxProximity="true">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="israel-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6180">Номер банковского счета для Израиль</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6180">Israel bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6181">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6181">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6182">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6182">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6183">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6183">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6184">Формат:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6184">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6185">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6185">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6186">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6186">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6187">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6187">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6188">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6188">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6189">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6189">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6190">Неформатированные:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6190">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6191">	13 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6191">13 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6192">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6192">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6193">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6193">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6194">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6194">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6195">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6195">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6196">регулярное выражение Regex_israel_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6196">The regular expression Regex_israel_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6197">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_israel_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6197">A keyword from Keyword_israel_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="7d08b2ff-a0b9-437f-957c-aeddbf9b2b25" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_israel_bank_account_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_israel_bank_account_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6198">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6198">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_israel_bank_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6199">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6199">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6200">Bank Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6200">Bank Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6201">Bank Account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6201">Bank Account</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6202">Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6202">Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6203">מספר חשבון בנק</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6203">מספר חשבון בנק</span></span> 
   
## <a name="israel-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6204">Национальный идентификационный номер для Израиля</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6204">Israel national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6205">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6205">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6206">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6206">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6207">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6207">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6208">девять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6208">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6209">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6209">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6210">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6210">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6211">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6211">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6212">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6212">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6213">функция Func_israeli_national_id_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6213">The function Func_israeli_national_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6214">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Israel_National_ID;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6214">A keyword from Keyword_Israel_National_ID is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6215">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6215">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel National ID Number -->
<Entity id="e05881f5-1db1-418c-89aa-a3ac5c5277ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_israeli_national_id_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Israel_National_ID" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6216">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6216">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_israel_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6217">Keyword_Israel_National_ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6217">Keyword_Israel_National_ID</span></span>

-   <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6218">מספר זהות</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6218">מספר זהות</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6219">מספר זיה וי</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6219">מספר זיה וי</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6220">מספר זיהוי ישר אלי</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6220">מספר זיהוי ישר אלי</span></span>      
-   <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6221">זהותישר אלית</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6221">זהותישר אלית</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6222">هو ية اسرائيل ية عدد</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6222">هو ية اسرائيل ية عدد</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6223">هوية إسرائ يلية</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6223">هوية إسرائ يلية</span></span>

-   <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6225">عدد هوية فريدة من نوعها</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6225">عدد هوية فريدة من نوعها</span></span>

## <a name="italy-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6234">Номер водительского удостоверения для Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6234">Italy driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6235">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6235">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6236">сочетание из 10 букв и цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6236">a combination of 10 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6237">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6237">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6238">сочетание из 10 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6238">a combination of 10 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6239">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6239">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6240">буква "A" или "V" (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6240">the letter "A" or "V" (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6241">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6241">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6242">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6242">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6243">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6243">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6244">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6244">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6245">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6245">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6246">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6246">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6247">регулярное выражение Regex_italy_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6247">The regular expression Regex_italy_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6248">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6248">A keyword from Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Italy Driver's license Number -->
<Entity id="97d6244f-9157-41bd-8e0c-9d669a5c4d71" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6249">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6249">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_italy_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6250">Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6250">Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6251">numero di patente</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6251">numero di patente</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6252">patente di guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6252">patente di guida</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6253">patente guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6253">patente guida</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6254">patenti di guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6254">patenti di guida</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6255">patenti guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6255">patenti guida</span></span>

## <a name="italy-fiscal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6256">Финансовый код Для Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6256">Italy fiscal code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6257">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6257">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6258">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6258">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6259">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6259">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6260">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6260">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6261">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6261">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6262">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6262">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6263">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6263">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6264">16-значное сочетание букв и цифр в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6264">a 16-character combination of letters and digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6265">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6265">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6266">16-значное сочетание букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6266">A 16-character combination of letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6267">три буквы, соответствующие первым трем consonants в имени семейства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6267">three letters that correspond to the first three consonants in the family name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6268">три буквы, соответствующие первому, третьему и четвертому consonants в первом имени</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6268">three letters that correspond to the first, third, and fourth consonants in the first name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6269">две цифры, соответствующие последним цифрам года рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6269">two digits that correspond to the last digits of the birth year</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6270">одна буква, соответствующая букве месяца рождения, буквы используются в алфавитном порядке, но используются только буквы A в E, H, L, M, P, R to T (таким образом, январь A, а октябрь — R)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6270">one letter that corresponds to the letter for the month of birth—letters are used in alphabetical order, but only the letters A to E, H, L, M, P, R to T are used (thus, January is A and October is R)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6271">две цифры, соответствующие дню месяца рождения, чтобы различать полы, 40 добавляется в день рождения для</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6271">two digits that correspond to the day of the month of birth—in order to differentiate between genders, 40 is added to the day of birth for women</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6272">четыре цифры, соответствующие коду региона, относя к замурованию человека (коды на территории страны используются для внешних стран)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6272">four digits that corresponds to the area code specific to the municipality where the person was born (country-wide codes are used for foreign countries)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6273">одна цифра четности</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6273">one parity digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6274">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6274">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6275">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6275">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6276">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6276">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6277">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6277">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6278">Функция находит  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6278">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6279">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6279">A keyword from  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6280">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6280">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6281">Функция находит  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6281">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Italy Fiscal Code -->
      <Entity id="4cd79172-8da9-4ff5-9188-98b1e7e2eca6" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="italy-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6316">Номер паспорта гражданина Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6316">Italy passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6317">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6317">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6318">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6318">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6319">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6319">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6320">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6320">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6321">две цифры или буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6321">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6322">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6322">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6323">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6323">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6324">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6324">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6325">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6325">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6326">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6326">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6327">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6327">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6328">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6328">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6329">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_italy_eu_passport_date` ДД MMM/MMM ГГ ГГ (пример — 01 GEN/JAN 1988) или находится ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6329">The regular expression `Regex_italy_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 01 GEN/JAN 1988) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6330">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6330">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6331">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6331">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6332">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6332">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Italy Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="39811019-4750-445f-b26d-4c0e6c431544" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number_common"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6334">Keywords_eu_passport_number_common</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6334">Keywords_eu_passport_number_common</span></span>

## <a name="italy-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6356">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость для Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6356">Italy value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6357">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6357">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6358">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6358">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6359">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6359">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6360">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6360">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6361">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6361">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6362">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6362">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6363">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6363">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6364">13-символьный буквонумерный шаблон с необязательными делетерами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6364">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6365">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6365">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6366">13 символов букв и цифр с необязательными разнородных символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6366">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6367">I или i</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6367">I or i</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6368">T или t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6368">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6369">дополнительное пространство, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6369">optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6370">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6370">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6371">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6371">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6372">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6372">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6373">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6373">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6374">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6374">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6375">Функция Func_italy_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6375">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6376">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6376">A keyword from Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6377">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6377">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6378">Функция Func_italy_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6378">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Italy Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="26a8cc07-2283-4a2a-ab1d-4ab643c4c67f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6379">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6379">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6380">Keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6380">Keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6382">vat no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6382">vat no</span></span>

## <a name="japan-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6386">Номер банковского счета для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6386">Japan bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6387">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6387">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6388">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6388">seven or eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6389">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6389">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6390">номер банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6390">bank account number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6391">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6391">seven or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6392">код филиала банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6392">bank account branch code:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6393">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6393">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6394">пробел или тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6394">a space or dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6395">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6395">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6396">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6396">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6397">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6397">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6398">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6398">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6399">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6399">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6400">Функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6400">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6401">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6401">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6402">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6402">One of the following is true:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6403">функция Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6403">The function Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6404">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6404">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6405">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6405">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6406">функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6406">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6407">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6407">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="d354f95b-96ee-4b80-80bc-4377312b55bc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Version minEngineVersion="15.01.0131.000">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
  </Version>    
     <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6455">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6455">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6456">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6456">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6457">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6457">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6458">12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6458">12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6459">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6459">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6460">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6460">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6461">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6461">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6462">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6462">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6463">функция Func_jp_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6463">The function Func_jp_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6464">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6464">A keyword from Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="c6011143-d087-451c-8313-7f6d4aed2270" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-my-number---corporate"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6502">Мой номер для Японии — корпоративный</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6502">Japan My Number - Corporate</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6503">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6503">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6504">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6504">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6505">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6505">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6506">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6506">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6507">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6507">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6508">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6508">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6509">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6509">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6510">13-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6510">13 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6511">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6511">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6512">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6512">13 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6513">одна цифра от одной до девяти</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6513">one digit from one to nine</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6514">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6514">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6515">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6515">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6516">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6516">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6517">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6517">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6518">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6518">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6519">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6519">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6520">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6520">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6521">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6521">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6522">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6522">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Corporate -->
      <Entity id="9e0eaf79-ff20-4ffb-b3e4-e7368d5db6ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6523">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6523">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_japan_my_number_corporate"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6524">Keyword_japan_my_number_corporate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6524">Keyword_japan_my_number_corporate</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6525">корпоративный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6525">corporate number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6526">マイナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6526">マイナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6527">共通番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6527">共通番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6528">マイナンバーカード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6528">マイナンバーカード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6529">マイナンバーカード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6529">マイナンバーカード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6530">個人番号カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6530">個人番号カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6531">個人識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6531">個人識別番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6532">個人識別ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6532">個人識別ナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6533">法人番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6533">法人番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6534">指定通知書</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6534">指定通知書</span></span>


## <a name="japan-my-number---personal"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6535">Мой номер для Японии — личный</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6535">Japan My Number - Personal</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6536">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6536">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6537">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6537">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6538">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6538">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6539">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6539">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6540">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6540">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6541">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6541">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6542">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6542">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6543">12-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6543">12 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6544">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6544">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6545">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6545">12 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6546">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6546">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6547">дополнительное пространство, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6547">an optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6548">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6548">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6549">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6549">an optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6550">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6550">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6551">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6551">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6552">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6552">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6553">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6553">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6554">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6554">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6555">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6555">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6556">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6556">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6557">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6557">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6558">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6558">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Personal -->
      <Entity id="98da8e66-7299-4ebd-9f82-c871ab37d3ef" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6559">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6559">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_japan_my_number_personal"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6560">Keyword_japan_my_number_personal</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6560">Keyword_japan_my_number_personal</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6561">мой номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6561">my number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6563">個人番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6563">個人番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6564">共通番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6564">共通番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6565">マイナンバーカード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6565">マイナンバーカード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6566">マイナンバーカード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6566">マイナンバーカード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6567">個人番号カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6567">個人番号カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6568">個人識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6568">個人識別番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6569">個人識別ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6569">個人識別ナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6570">通知カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6570">通知カード</span></span>

   
## <a name="japan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6571">Номер паспорта гражданина Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6571">Japan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6572">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6572">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6573">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6573">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6574">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6574">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6575">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), за которыми следуют семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6575">two letters (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6576">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6576">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6577">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6577">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6578">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6578">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6579">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6579">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6580">функция Func_jp_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6580">The function Func_jp_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6581">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6581">A keyword from Keyword_jp_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="75177310-1a09-4613-bf6d-833aae3743f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_passport" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6582">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6582">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_passport"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6583">Keyword_jp_passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6583">Keyword_jp_passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6584">Passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6584">Passport</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6585">Passport Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6585">Passport Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6586">Passport No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6586">Passport No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6587">Passport#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6587">Passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6588">パスポート</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6588">パスポート</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6589">パスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6589">パスポート番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6590">パスポートナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6590">パスポートナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6591">パスポート#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6591">パスポート＃</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6592">パスポート #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6592">パスポート#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6593">パポ>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6593">パスポートNo.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6594">旅券番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6594">旅券番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6595">旅券番号#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6595">旅券番号＃</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6596">旅券番号♯</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6596">旅券番号♯</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6597">旅券ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6597">旅券ナンバー</span></span>


## <a name="japan-residence-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6598">Номер карты для проживания в Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6598">Japan residence card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6599">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6599">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6600">12 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6600">12 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6601">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6601">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6602">12 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6602">12 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6603">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6603">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6604">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6604">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6605">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6605">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6606">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6606">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6607">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6607">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6608">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6608">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6609">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6609">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6610">Регулярное выражение Regex_jp_residence_card_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6610">The regular expression Regex_jp_residence_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6611">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_residence_card_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6611">A keyword from Keyword_jp_residence_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Japan Residence Card Number-->
-<Entity id="ac36fef2-a289-4e2c-bb48-b02366e89fc0" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_jp_residence_card_number"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_residence_card_number"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6612">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6612">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="japan-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6620">Номер регистрации резидента Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6620">Japan resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6621">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6621">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6622">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6622">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6623">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6623">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6624">11 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6624">11 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6625">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6625">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6626">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6626">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6627">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6627">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6628">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6628">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6629">функция Func_jp_resident_registration_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6629">The function Func_jp_resident_registration_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6630">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6630">A keyword from Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="01c1209b-6389-4faf-a5f8-3f7e13899652" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_resident_registration_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6631">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6631">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6637">Residents Basic Registry No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6637">Residents Basic Registry No.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6639">外国人登録証明書番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6639">外国人登録証明書番号</span></span>

## <a name="japan-social-insurance-number-sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6643">Номер социального страхования для Японии (SIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6643">Japan social insurance number (SIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6644">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6644">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6645">7–12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6645">7-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6646">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6646">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6647">7–12 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6647">7-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6648">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6648">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6649">дефис (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6649">a hyphen (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6650">шесть цифр ИЛИ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6650">six digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6651">7–12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6651">7-12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6652">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6652">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6653">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6653">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6654">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6654">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6655">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6655">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6656">функция Func_jp_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6656">The function Func_jp_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6657">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6657">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6658">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6658">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6659">функция Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6659">The function Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6660">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6660">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="c840e719-0896-45bb-84fd-1ed5c95e45ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin_pre_1997" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="latvia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6681">Номер водительского удостоверения для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6681">Latvia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6682">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6682">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6683">три буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6683">three letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6684">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6684">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6685">три буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6685">three letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6686">три буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6686">three letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6687">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6687">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6688">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6688">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6689">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6689">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6690">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6690">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6691">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6691">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6692">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6692">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6693">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6693">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="ec996de0-30f2-46b1-b192-4d2ff8805fa7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
