- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6703">driver lics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6703">driver lics</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6704">driver license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6704">driver license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6705">driver licenses</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6705">driver licenses</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6707">driver licences</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6707">driver licences</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6708">driverslic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6708">driverslic</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6709">driverslics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6709">driverslics</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6710">driverslicence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6710">driverslicence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6711">driverslicences</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6711">driverslicences</span></span>

## <a name="latvia-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6818">Персональный код для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6818">Latvia personal code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6819">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6819">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6820">11 цифр и необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6820">11 digits and an optional hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6821">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6821">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6822">Старый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6822">Old format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6823">11 цифр и дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6823">11 digits and a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6824">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ДДММАЙ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6824">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6825">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6825">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6826">одна цифра, соответствующая годовщине рождения ("0" для 19-го, "1" для 20-го и "2" для 21-го)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6826">one digit that corresponds to the century of birth ("0" for 19th century, "1" for 20th century, and "2" for 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6827">четыре цифры, генерируемые случайным образом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6827">four digits, randomly generated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6828">Новый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6828">New format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6829">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6829">11 digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6830">Две цифры "32"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6830">Two digits "32"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6831">девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6831">Nine digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6832">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6832">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6833">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6833">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6834">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6834">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6835">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6835">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6836">Функция или  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` regex находит `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6836">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6837">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6837">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6838">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6838">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6839">Функция или  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` regex находит `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6839">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="03fcf763-27c2-49ed-9422-2641c6c895c9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="latvia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6902">Номер паспорта гражданина Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6902">Latvia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6903">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6903">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6904">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6904">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6905">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6905">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6906">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6906">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6907">две цифры или буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6907">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6908">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6908">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6909">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6909">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6910">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6910">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6911">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6911">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6912">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6912">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6913">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6913">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6914">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6914">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6915">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_eu_passport_date1` ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6915">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6916">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6916">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6917">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6917">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6918">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6918">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="23ae25ec-cc28-421b-b77a-3054eadf1ede" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6941">Номер водительского удостоверения для Литвы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6941">Lithuania driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6942">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6942">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6943">восемь цифр без пробелов и делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6943">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6944">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6944">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6945">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6945">eight digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6946">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6946">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6947">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6947">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6948">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6948">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6949">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6949">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6950">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6950">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-6951">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-6951">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="86f7628b-e0f4-4dc3-9fbc-e4300e4c7d78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7076">Персональный код Для Литвы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7076">Lithuania personal code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7077">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7077">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7078">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7078">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7079">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7079">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7080">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7080">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7081">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7081">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7082">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7082">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7083">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7083">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7084">11 цифр без пробелов и делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7084">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7085">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7085">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7086">11 цифр без пробелов и селитров:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7086">11 digits without spaces and delimiters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7087">одна цифра (1–6), соответствующая полу и возрасту человека при рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7087">one digit (1-6) that corresponds to the person's gender and century of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7088">шесть цифр, соответствующие дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7088">six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7089">три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру даты рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7089">three digits that correspond to the serial number of the date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7090">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7090">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7091">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7091">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7092">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7092">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7093">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7093">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7094">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7094">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7095">Функция находит  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7095">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7096">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7096">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7097">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7097">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7098">Функция находит  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7098">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="cd6d3786-8ec3-4524-a2cf-1e0095379171" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7133">Номер паспорта гражданина Литвы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7133">Lithuania passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7134">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7134">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7135">восемь цифр или букв без пробелов или селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7135">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7136">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7136">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7137">восемь цифр или букв (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7137">eight digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7138">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7138">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7139">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7139">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7140">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7140">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7141">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7141">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7142">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7142">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7143">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7143">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7144">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date3` находит дату в формате ДД ММ YYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7144">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7145">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7145">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7146">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7146">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7147">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7147">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="1b79900f-047b-4c3f-846f-7d73b5534bce" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7167">Номер водительского удостоверения Химмхета</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7167">Luxemburg driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7168">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7168">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7169">шесть цифр без пробелов и делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7169">six digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7170">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7170">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7171">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7171">six digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7172">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7172">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7173">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7173">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7174">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7174">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7175">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7175">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7176">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7176">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7177">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7177">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="89daf717-1544-4860-9a2e-fc9166dd8852" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7301">Национальный идентификационный номер (естественные лица) для Нюксемнеса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7301">Luxemburg national identification number (natural persons)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7302">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7302">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7303">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7303">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7304">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7304">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7305">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7305">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7306">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7306">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7307">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7307">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7308">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7308">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7309">13 цифр без пробелов или селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7309">13 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7310">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7310">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7311">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7311">13 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7312">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7312">11 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7313">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7313">two check digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7314">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7314">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7315">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7315">yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7316">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7316">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7317">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7317">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7318">Функция находит  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7318">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7319">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7319">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7320">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7320">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7321">Функция находит  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7321">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 


```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="aaf661ed-29ec-426d-8bf9-880cad298ebb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7344">Номер паспорта Химмхета</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7344">Luxemburg passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7345">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7345">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7346">восемь цифр или букв без пробелов или селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7346">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7347">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7347">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7348">восемь цифр или букв (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7348">eight digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7349">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7349">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7350">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7350">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7351">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7351">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7352">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7352">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7353">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7353">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7354">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7354">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7355">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date3` находит дату в формате ДД ММ YYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7355">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7356">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7356">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7357">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7357">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7358">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7358">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="81d5c027-bed9-4421-91a0-3b2e55b3eb85" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7359">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7359">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7360">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7360">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7361">passport #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7361">passport#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7362">passport #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7362">passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7363">passportid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7363">passportid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7364">passports</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7364">passports</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7365">passportno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7365">passportno</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7366">passport no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7366">passport no</span></span>

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-non-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7390">Национальный идентификационный номер для Фемнеса (не является лицом)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7390">Luxemburg national identification number (non natural persons)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7391">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7391">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7392">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7392">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7393">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7393">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7394">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7394">11 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7395">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7395">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7396">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7396">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7397">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7397">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7398">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7398">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7399">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7399">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7400">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7400">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7401">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7401">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7402">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7402">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7403">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7403">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7404">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7404">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7405">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7405">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7406">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7406">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7407">Функция находит  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7407">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7408">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7408">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7409">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7409">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7410">Функция находит  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7410">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Non-natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="84bffa3a-d805-4788-a613-b1e4df3804cf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malaysia-identification-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7450">Номер идентификационных карт для Малайзии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7450">Malaysia identification card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7451">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7451">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7452">12 цифр, содержащих необязательные дефисы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7452">12 digits containing optional hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7453">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7453">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7454">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7454">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7455">шесть цифр в формате YYMMDD, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7455">six digits in the format YYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7456">Тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7456">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7457">двух буквный код места рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7457">two-letter place-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7458">Тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7458">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7459">три случайные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7459">three random digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7460">однозначный код пола</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7460">one-digit gender code</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7461">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7461">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7462">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7462">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7463">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7463">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7464">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7464">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7465">регулярное выражение Regex_malaysia_id_card_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7465">The regular expression Regex_malaysia_id_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7466">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7466">A keyword from Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Malaysia ID Card Number -->
</Entity>
      <Entity id="7f0e921c-9677-435b-aba2-bb8f1013c749" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malaysia_id_card_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7467">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7467">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_malaysia_id_card_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7468">Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7468">Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7469">цифровая карточка приложения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7469">digital application card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7470">i/c</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7470">i/c</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7471">i/c no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7471">i/c no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7472">ic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7472">ic</span></span>

## <a name="malta-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7493">Номер водительского удостоверения для Мальты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7493">Malta driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7494">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7494">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7495">Сочетание двух символов и шести цифр в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7495">Combination of two characters and six digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7496">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7496">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7497">сочетание двух символов и шести цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7497">combination of two characters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7498">два символа (цифры или буквы без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7498">two characters (digits or letters, not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7499">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7499">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7500">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7500">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7501">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7501">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7502">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7502">three digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7503">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7503">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7504">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7504">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7505">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7505">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7506">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7506">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7507">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7507">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7508">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7508">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="a3bdaa4a-8371-4735-8fa5-56ee0fb4afc4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7632">Номер удостоверения личности для Мальты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7632">Malta identity card number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7633">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7633">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7634">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7634">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7635">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7635">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7636">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7636">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7637">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7637">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7638">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7638">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7639">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7639">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7640">семь цифр, за которыми следует одна буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7640">seven digits followed by one letter</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7641">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7641">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7642">семь цифр, за которыми следует одна буква:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7642">seven digits followed by one letter:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7643">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7643">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7644">одна буква в "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (без чувствительность к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7644">one letter in "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (case insensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7645">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7645">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7646">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7646">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7647">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7647">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7648">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7648">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7649">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7649">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7650">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7650">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7651">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7651">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7652">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7652">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Identity Card Number -->
      <Entity id="854b36b3-a388-4ac8-a4ec-677c2b5e4356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7661">numru ta 'identifzzjoni uniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7661">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni uniku</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7662">numru ta' identità uniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7662">numru ta' identità uniku</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7663">numru tas-servizz taċ-ċittadin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7663">numru tas-servizz taċ-ċittadin</span></span>

## <a name="malta-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7669">Номер паспорта гражданина Мальты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7669">Malta passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7670">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7670">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7671">семь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7671">seven digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7672">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7672">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7673">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7673">seven digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7674">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7674">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7675">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7675">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7676">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7676">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7677">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7677">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7678">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7678">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7679">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7679">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7680">Найдено ключевое `Keywords_eu_passport_date` слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7680">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7681">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7681">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7682">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7682">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7683">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7683">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="b2b21198-48f9-4d13-b2a5-03969bff0fb8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7684">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7684">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="malta-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7703">Идентификационный номер налога на Мальте</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7703">Malta tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7704">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7704">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7705">Для граждан Тайваня:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7705">For Maltese nationals:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7706">семь цифр и одна буква в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7706">seven digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7707">Неконтюзские граждане и подмайства:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7707">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7708">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7708">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7709">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7709">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7710">Граждане Тайваня: семь цифр и одна буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7710">Maltese nationals: seven digits and one letter</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7711">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7711">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7712">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7712">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7713">Нефрумовские граждане и сущностями, не относягими к сша: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7713">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities: nine digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7714">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7714">nine digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7715">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7715">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7716">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7716">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7717">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7717">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7718">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7718">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7719">Regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  или `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7719">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7720">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7720">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7721">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7721">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7722">Regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` или `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7722">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Tax ID Number -->
      <Entity id="ec830c63-65f4-45d0-9d8c-910dc8334b20" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-citizens-service-bsn-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7755">Номер службы гражданина Нидерландов (BSN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7755">Netherlands citizen's service (BSN) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7756">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7756">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7757">восемь-девять цифр, содержащих необязательные пробелы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7757">eight-nine digits containing optional spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7758">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7758">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7759">восемь-девять цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7759">eight-nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7760">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7760">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7761">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7761">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7762">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7762">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7763">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7763">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7764">две-три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7764">two-three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7765">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7765">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7766">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7766">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7767">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7767">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7768">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7768">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7769">функция Func_netherlands_bsn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7769">The function Func_netherlands_bsn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7770">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_netherlands_bsn;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7770">A keyword from Keyword_netherlands_bsn is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7771">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7771">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Citizen's Service (BSN) Number -->
      <Entity id="c5f54253-ef7e-44f6-a578-440ed67e946d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_bsn" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7788">sofi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7788">sofi</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7794">uniqueidentityno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7794">uniqueidentityno#</span></span>

## <a name="netherlands-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7795">Номер водительского удостоверения для Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7795">Netherlands driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7796">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7796">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7797">десять цифр без пробелов и делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7797">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7798">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7798">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7799">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7799">ten digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7800">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7800">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7801">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7801">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7802">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7802">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7803">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7803">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7804">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7804">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7805">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7805">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="6247fbea-ab80-4be5-8233-308b7c031401" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7933">Номер паспорта гражданина Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7933">Netherlands passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7934">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7934">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7935">девять букв или цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7935">nine letters or digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7936">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7936">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7937">девять букв или цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7937">nine letters or digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7938">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7938">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7939">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7939">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7940">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7940">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7941">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7941">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7942">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7942">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7943">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7943">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7944">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date` ДД MMM/MMM YYYY (пример — 26 MAA/MAR 2012)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7944">The regular expression `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format  DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 26 MAA/MAR 2012)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7945">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7945">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7946">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7946">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7947">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7947">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="61786727-bafd-45f6-94d9-888d815e228e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
