## <a name="netherlands-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7965">Налоговый идентификационный номер для Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7965">Netherlands tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7966">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7966">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7967">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7967">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7968">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7968">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7969">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7969">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7970">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7970">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7971">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7971">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7972">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7972">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7973">девять цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7973">nine digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7974">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7974">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7975">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7975">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7976">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7976">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7977">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7977">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7978">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7978">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7979">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7979">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7980">Функция находит  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7980">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7981">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7981">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7982">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7982">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-7983">Функция находит  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-7983">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="01f42a64-eba7-4892-a67b-398237e4ade2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8021">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость для Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8021">Netherlands value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8022">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8022">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8023">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8023">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8024">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8024">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8025">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8025">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8026">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8026">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8027">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8027">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8028">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8028">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8029">14-символьный буквонумерный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8029">14 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8030">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8030">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8031">14-символьный буквонумерный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8031">14-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8032">N или n</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8032">N or n</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8033">L или l</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8033">L or l</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8034">дополнительное пространство, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8034">optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8035">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8035">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8036">дополнительное пространство, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8036">optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8037">B или b</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8037">B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8038">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8038">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8039">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8039">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8040">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8040">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8041">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8041">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8042">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8042">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8043">Функция Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8043">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8044">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8044">A keyword from Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8045">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8045">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8046">Функция Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8046">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="4f320d9b-4972-41ae-b337-88d499bb1ade" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8047">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8047">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_netherlands_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8048">Keyword_netherlands_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8048">Keyword_netherlands_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8049">номер плательщика НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8049">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8050">vat no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8050">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8051">vat #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8051">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8052">налоговый возврат на носимый tafoege</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8052">wearde tafoege tax getal</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8053">btw n уmer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8053">btw nûmer</span></span>

## <a name="new-zealand-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8055">Номер банковского счета для Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8055">New Zealand bank account number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8056">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8056">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8057">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8057">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8058">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8058">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8059">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8059">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8060">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8060">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8061">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8061">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8062">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8062">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8063">Шаблон из 14-16 цифр с необязательными делегаторами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8063">14 to 16 digit pattern with optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8064">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8064">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8065">Шаблон из 14–16 цифр с необязательными делегаторами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8065">14 to 16 digit pattern with optional delimiter:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8066">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8066">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8067">необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8067">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8068">три-четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8068">three to four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8069">необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8069">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8070">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8070">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8071">необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8071">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8072">две-три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8072">two to three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8073">дефис или пробел для параметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8073">an options hyphen or space</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8074">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8074">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8075">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8075">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8076">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8076">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8077">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8077">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8078">Функция Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8078">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8079">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8079">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8080">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8080">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8081">Функция Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8081">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Bank Account Number -->
      <Entity id="1a97fc2b-dd2f-48f1-bc4e-2ddf25813956" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zFealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="new-zealand-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8089">Номер водительского удостоверения для Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8089">New Zealand driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8090">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8090">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8091">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8091">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8092">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8092">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8093">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8093">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8094">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8094">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8095">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8095">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8096">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8096">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8097">восьми символьный букво-цифровая схема</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8097">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8098">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8098">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8099">восьми символьный букво-цифровая схема</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8099">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8100">две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8100">two letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8101">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8101">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8102">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8102">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8103">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8103">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8104">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8104">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8105">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8105">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8106">Функция Func_newzealand_driver_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8106">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8107">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8107">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8108">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8108">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8109">Функция Func_newzealand_driver_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8109">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Driver License Number -->
      <Entity id="1924b377-d287-49c9-a737-cfe7a8a2615a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>

```

## <a name="new-zealand-inland-revenue-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8176">Число внутренних доходов для Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8176">New Zealand inland revenue number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8177">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8177">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8178">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8178">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8179">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8179">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8180">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8180">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8181">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8181">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8182">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8182">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8183">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8183">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8184">восемь или девять цифр с необязательными делегаторами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8184">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8185">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8185">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8186">восемь или девять цифр с необязательными делегаторами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8186">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8187">две или три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8187">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8188">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8188">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8189">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8189">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8190">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8190">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8191">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8191">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8192">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8192">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8193">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8193">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8194">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8194">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8195">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8195">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8196">Функция Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8196">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8197">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8197">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8198">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8198">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8199">Функция Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8199">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Inland Revenue Number -->
      <Entity id="dd0fe2bc-7bcf-455f-bac1-83b1e3eb25fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8201">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8201">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span></span>

## <a name="new-zealand-ministry-of-health-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8208">Министерство здравоохранения Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8208">New Zealand ministry of health number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8209">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8209">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8210">три буквы, пробел (необязательно) и четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8210">three letters, a space (optional), and four digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8211">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8211">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8212">три буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), кроме "I" и "O"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8212">three letters (not case sensitive) except 'I' and 'O'</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8213">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8213">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8214">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8214">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8215">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8215">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8216">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8216">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8217">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8217">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8218">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8218">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8219">функция Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8219">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8220">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_nz_terms;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8220">A keyword from Keyword_nz_terms is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8221">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8221">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8222">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8222">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8223">функция Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8223">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8224">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8224">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- New Zealand Health Number -->
    <Entity id="2b71c1c8-d14e-4430-82dc-fd1ed6bf05c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_nz_terms" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
       </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="new-zealand-social-wlefare-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8238">Номер социальной сети Для Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8238">New Zealand social wlefare number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8239">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8239">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8240">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8240">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8241">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8241">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8242">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8242">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8243">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8243">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8244">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8244">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8245">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8245">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8246">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8246">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8247">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8247">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8248">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8248">nine digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8249">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8249">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8250">необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8250">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8251">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8251">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8252">необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8252">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8253">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8253">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8254">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8254">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8255">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8255">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8256">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8256">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8257">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8257">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8258">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8258">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8259">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8259">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8260">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8260">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8261">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8261">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Newzealand Social Welfare Number -->
      <Entity id="20f3c48d-4ac1-4cd2-86bd-34ecc1826e9d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8262">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8262">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8263">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8263">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8264">социальные сети #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8264">social welfare #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8265">социальные сети #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8265">social welfare#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8266">social welfare No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8266">social welfare No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8267">номер социальных сетей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8267">social welfare number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8268">swn #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8268">swn#</span></span>

   
## <a name="norway-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8269">Идентификационный номер для Норвегии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8269">Norway identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8270">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8270">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8271">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8271">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8272">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8272">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8273">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8273">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8274">шесть цифр в формате ДДММАЙ, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8274">six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8275">трехзначный индивидуальный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8275">three-digit individual number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8276">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8276">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8277">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8277">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8278">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8278">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8279">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8279">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8280">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8280">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8281">функция Func_norway_id_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8281">The function Func_norway_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8282">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_norway_id_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8282">A keyword from Keyword_norway_id_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8283">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8283">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8284">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8284">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8285">функция Func_norway_id_numbe находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8285">The function Func_norway_id_numbe finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8286">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8286">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Norway Identification Number -->
<Entity id="d4c8a798-e9f2-4bd3-9652-500d24080fc3" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8287">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8287">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_norway_id_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8288">Keyword_norway_id_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8288">Keyword_norway_id_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8289">Personal identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8289">Personal identification number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8291">ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8291">ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8292">Идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8292">Identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8293">Personnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8293">Personnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8294">Fфdselsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8294">Fødselsnummer</span></span>

   
## <a name="philippines-unified-multi-purpose-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8295">Единый многонамерный идентификационный номер для Филиппин</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8295">Philippines unified multi-purpose identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8296">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8296">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8297">12 цифр, разделенных дефисами.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8297">12 digits separated by hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8298">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8298">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8299">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8299">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8300">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8300">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8301">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8301">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8302">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8302">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8303">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8303">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8304">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8304">one digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8305">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8305">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8306">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8306">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8307">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8307">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8308">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8308">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8309">регулярное выражение Regex_philippines_unified_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8309">The regular expression Regex_philippines_unified_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8310">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_philippines_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8310">A keyword from Keyword_philippines_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Philippines Unified Multi-Purpose ID number -->
<Entity id="019b39dd-8c25-4765-91a3-d9c6baf3c3b3" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_philippines_unified_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_philippines_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8311">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8311">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_philippines_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8312">Keyword_philippines_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8312">Keyword_philippines_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8313">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8313">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8314">UMID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8314">UMID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8315">Identity Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8315">Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8316">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8316">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span></span>

## <a name="poland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8317">Номер водительского удостоверения для Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8317">Poland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8318">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8318">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8319">14 цифр, содержащих 2 косые черты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8319">14 digits containing 2 forward slashes</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8320">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8320">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8321">14 цифр и 2 косой черты:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8321">14 digits and 2 forward slashes:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8322">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8322">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8323">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8323">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8324">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8324">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8325">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8325">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8326">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8326">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8327">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8327">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8328">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8328">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8329">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8329">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8330">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8330">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8331">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8331">The regular expression  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8332">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8332">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Poland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="24d51f99-ee9e-4060-a077-cae58cab1ee4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8456">Удостоверение личности для Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8456">Poland identity card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8457">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8457">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8458">три буквы и шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8458">three letters and six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8459">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8459">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8460">три буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8460">three letters (not case sensitive) followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8461">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8461">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8462">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8462">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8463">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8463">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8464">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8464">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8465">функция Func_polish_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8465">The function Func_polish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8466">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8466">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8467">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8467">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Identity Card-->
<Entity id="25E64989-ED5D-40CA-A939-6C14183BB7BF" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8468">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8468">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8469">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8469">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8470">Dowód osobisty</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8470">Dowód osobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8471">Numer dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8471">Numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8472">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8472">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8473">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8473">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8474">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8474">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8475">Dowód Tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8475">Dowód Tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8476">dow.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8476">dow.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8477">os.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8477">os.</span></span>

   
## <a name="poland-national-id-pesel"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8478">Национальный ИД для Польша (PESEL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8478">Poland national ID (PESEL)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8479">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8479">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8480">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8480">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8481">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8481">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8482">6 цифр, представляющих дату рождения в формате YYMMDD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8482">6 digits representing date of birth in the format YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8483">4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8483">4 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8484">1 контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8484">1 check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8485">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8485">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8486">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8486">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8487">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8487">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8488">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8488">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8489">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8489">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8490">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_pesel_identification_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8490">A keyword from Keyword_pesel_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8491">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8491">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8492">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8492">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8493">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8493">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8494">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8494">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Poland National ID (PESEL) -->
      <Entity id="E3AAF206-4297-412F-9E06-BA8487E22456" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8495">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8495">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8499">niepowtarzalny numer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8499">niepowtarzalny numer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8500">niepowtarzalnynumer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8500">niepowtarzalnynumer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8501">nr.-pesel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8501">nr.-pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8502">nr-pesel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8502">nr-pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8503">numer identyfcyjny</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8503">numer identyfikacyjny</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8504">pesel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8504">pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8505">tosamoraswej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8505">tożsamości narodowej</span></span>

   
## <a name="poland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8506">Номер паспорта гражданина Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8506">Poland passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8507">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ес и доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8507">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8508">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8508">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8509">две буквы и семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8509">two letters and seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8510">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8510">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8511">Две буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8511">Two letters (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8512">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8512">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8513">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8513">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8514">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8514">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8515">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8515">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8516">функция Func_polish_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8516">The function Func_polish_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8517">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8517">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8518">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8518">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Passport Number -->
<Entity id="03937FB5-D2B6-4487-B61F-0F8BFF7C3517" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
</Version>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8519">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8519">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8520">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8520">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span></span>

## <a name="poland-regon-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8525">Номер REGON для Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8525">Poland REGON number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8526">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8526">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8527">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8527">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8528">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8528">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8529">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8529">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8530">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8530">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8531">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8531">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8532">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8532">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8533">девятизначный или 14-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8533">nine digit or 14 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8534">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8534">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8535">девятизначное или 14-значное число:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8535">nine digit or 14-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8536">девять цифр или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8536">nine digits or</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8537">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8537">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8538">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8538">hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8539">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8539">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8540">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8540">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8541">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8541">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8542">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8542">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8543">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8543">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8544">Функция Func_polish_regon_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8544">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8545">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_polish_regon_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8545">A keyword from Keywords_polish_regon_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8546">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8546">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8547">Функция Func_polish_regon_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8547">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Polish REGON Number  -->
      <Entity id="fc87b421-f437-4f8b-b739-29a735ead0d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8552">статистический ид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8552">statistical id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8553">статистический нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8553">statistical no</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8556">regonno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8556">regonno#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8559">companyidno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8559">companyidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8560">numer statystyczny</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8560">numer statystyczny</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8561">numeru regon</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8561">numeru regon</span></span>

## <a name="poland-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8564">Налоговый идентификационный номер для Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8564">Poland tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8565">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8565">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8566">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8566">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8567">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8567">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8568">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8568">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8569">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8569">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8570">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8570">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8571">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8571">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8572">11 цифр без пробелов или селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8572">11 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8573">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8573">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8574">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8574">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8575">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8575">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8576">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8576">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8577">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8577">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8578">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8578">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8579">Функция находит  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8579">The function  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8580">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8580">A keyword from  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
  
```xml
      <!-- Poland Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="1ff28b4d-40f2-49e9-b677-9606a88e2bca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-citizen-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8610">Номер карты гражданина Португалии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8610">Portugal citizen card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8611">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8611">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8612">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8612">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8613">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8613">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8614">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8614">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8615">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8615">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8616">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8616">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8617">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8617">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8618">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8618">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8619">регулярное выражение Regex_portugal_citizen_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8619">The regular expression Regex_portugal_citizen_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-8620">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_portugal_citizen_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-8620">A keyword from Keyword_portugal_citizen_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Portugal Citizen Card Number -->
<Entity id="91a7ece2-add4-4986-9a15-c84544d81ecd" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_citizen_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_portugal_citizen_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
