- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10607">Zhōnghuá Mínguó hùzhào</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10607">Zhōnghuá Mínguó hùzhào</span></span>
   
## <a name="taiwan-resident-certificate-arctarc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10608">Номер сертификата резидента Тайваня (ARC/TARC)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10608">Taiwan resident certificate (ARC/TARC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10609">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10609">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10610">десять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10610">ten letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10611">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10611">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10612">десять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10612">ten letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10613">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10613">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10614">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10614">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10615">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10615">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10616">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10616">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10617">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10617">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10618">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10618">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10619">регулярное выражение Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10619">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10620">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10620">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Resident Certificate (ARC/TARC) -->
<Entity id="48269fec-05ea-46ea-b326-f5623a58c6e9" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10621">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10621">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10633">台灣地區居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10633">台灣地區居留證</span></span> 

## <a name="thai-population-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10634">Идентификационный код для тайских пользователей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10634">Thai population identification code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10635">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10635">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10636">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10636">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10637">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10637">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10638">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10638">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10639">первая цифра не ноль или девять</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10639">first digit is not zero  or nine</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10640">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10640">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10641">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10641">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10642">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10642">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10643">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10643">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10644">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10644">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10645">Функция Func_Thai_Citizen_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10645">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10646">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10646">A keyword from Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10647">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10647">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10648">Функция Func_Thai_Citizen_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10648">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Thai Citizen ID -->
-<Entity id="44ca9e86-ead7-4c5d-884a-e2eaa401515e" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10649">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10649">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_thai_citizen_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10650">Keyword_thai_citizen_Id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10650">Keyword_thai_citizen_Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10651">ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10651">ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10652">Идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10652">Identification Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10653">บัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10653">บัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10654">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10654">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10655">บัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10655">บัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10656">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10656">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span></span>
  
## <a name="turkish-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10657">Идентификационный номер гражданина Турецкий</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10657">Turkish national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10658">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10658">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10659">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10659">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10660">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10660">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10661">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10661">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10662">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10662">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10663">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10663">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10664">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10664">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10665">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10665">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10666">Функция Func_Turkish_National_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10666">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10667">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Turkish_National_Id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10667">A keyword from Keyword_Turkish_National_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10668">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10668">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10669">Функция Func_Turkish_National_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10669">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Turkish National Identity -->
-<Entity id="fb621f20-3876-4cfc-acec-8c8e73ca32c7" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10670">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10670">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_turkish_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10671">Keyword_turkish_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10671">Keyword_turkish_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10672">TC Kim kim</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10672">TC Kimlik No</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10673">TC Kim numaras TC Kimmaras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10673">TC Kimlik numarası</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10674">Vatanda vat vatk numaras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10674">Vatandaşlık numarası</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10675">Vatanda vat vatk no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10675">Vatandaşlık no</span></span>

## <a name="uk-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10676">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10676">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10677">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10677">driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10678">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации номера водительского удостоверения ЕС и доступен в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10678">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10679">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10679">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10680">Сочетание 18 букв и цифр в указанном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10680">Combination of 18 letters and digits in the specified format</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10681">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10681">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10682">18 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10682">18 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10683">пять букв (без чувствительность к букве) или цифра "9" в качестве буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10683">five letters (not case sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10684">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10684">one digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10685">пять цифр в формате даты MMDDY для даты рождения (7-й знак приращен на 50, если драйвер — женщина, то есть от 51 до 62 вместо 01–12)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10685">five digits in the date format MMDDY for date of birth (7th character is incremented by 50 if driver is female, i.e. 51 to 62 instead of 01 to 12)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10686">две буквы (без чувствительность к букве) или цифра "9" в качестве буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10686">two letters (not case sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10687">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10687">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10688">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10688">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10689">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10689">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10690">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10690">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10691">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10691">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10692">функция Func_uk_drivers_license находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10692">The function Func_uk_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10693">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_drivers_license;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10693">A keyword from Keyword_uk_drivers_license is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10694">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10694">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="f93de4be-d94c-40df-a8be-461738047551" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_drivers_license" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10695">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10695">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10697">DVLA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10697">DVLA</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10700">motor cars</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10700">motor cars</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10701">125cc</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10701">125cc</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10702">sidecar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10702">sidecar</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10703">трициклы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10703">tricycles</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10704">ы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10704">motorcycles</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10705">photocard licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10705">photocard licence</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10706">learner drivers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10706">learner drivers</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10707">licence holder</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10707">licence holder</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10708">licence holders</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10708">licence holders</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10709">driving licences</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10709">driving licences</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10710">driving licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10710">driving licence</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10711">dual control car</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10711">dual control car</span></span> 
   
## <a name="uk-electoral-roll-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10712">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10712">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10713">roll number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10713">electoral roll number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10714">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10714">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10715">две буквы, за которыми следуют 1–4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10715">two letters followed by 1-4 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10716">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10716">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10717">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), за которыми следуют 1–4 числа</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10717">two letters (not case sensitive) followed by 1-4 numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10718">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10718">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10719">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10719">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10720">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10720">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10721">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10721">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10722">регулярное выражение Regex_uk_electoral находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10722">The regular expression Regex_uk_electoral finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10723">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_electoral.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10723">A keyword from Keyword_uk_electoral is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Electoral Number -->
<Entity id="a3eea206-dc0c-4f06-9e22-aa1be3059963" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_uk_electoral" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_electoral" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10724">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10724">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_electoral"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10725">Keyword_uk_electoral</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10725">Keyword_uk_electoral</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10726">council nomination</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10726">council nomination</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10727">nomination form</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10727">nomination form</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10728">electoral register</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10728">electoral register</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10729">electoral roll</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10729">electoral roll</span></span>

   
## <a name="uk-national-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10730">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10730">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10731">national health service number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10731">national health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10732">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10732">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10733">10–17 цифр, разделенных пробелами.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10733">10-17 digits separated by spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10734">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10734">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10735">10-17 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10735">10-17 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10736">три или десять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10736">either three or ten digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10737">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10737">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10738">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10738">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10739">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10739">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10740">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10740">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10741">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10741">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10742">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10742">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10743">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10743">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10744">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10744">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10745">Функция Func_uk_nhs_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10745">The function Func_uk_nhs_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10746">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10746">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10747">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10747">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10748">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number1;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10748">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number1 is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10749">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10749">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10750">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10750">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. NHS Number -->
<Entity id="3192014e-2a16-44e9-aa69-4b20375c9a78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nhs_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number1" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="uk-national-insurance-number-nino"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10768">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10768">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10769">national insurance number (NINO)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10769">national insurance number (NINO)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10770">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации "Номер государственного номера для ЕС" и доступен в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10770">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identificaiton Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10771">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10771">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10772">семь или девять символов, разделенных пробелами или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10772">seven characters or nine characters separated by spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10773">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10773">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10774">два возможных шаблона:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10774">two possible patterns:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10775">две буквы (допустимые niNOs используют только определенные символы в этом префиксе, который проверяется этим шаблоном; без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10775">two letters (valid NINOs use only certain characters in this prefix, which this pattern validates; not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10776">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10776">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10777">либо "A", "B", "C", либо "D" (как и префикс, в суффиксе разрешены только определенные символы, без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10777">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D' (like the prefix, only certain characters are allowed in the suffix; not case sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10778">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10778">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10779">две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10779">two letters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10780">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10780">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10781">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10781">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10782">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10782">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10783">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10783">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10784">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10784">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10785">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10785">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10786">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10786">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10787">"A", "B", "C" или "D"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10787">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D'</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10788">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10788">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10789">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10789">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10790">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10790">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10791">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10791">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10792">функция Func_uk_nino находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10792">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10793">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nino.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10793">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nino is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10794">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10794">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10795">функция Func_uk_nino находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10795">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.K. NINO -->
    <Entity id="16c07343-c26f-49d2-a987-3daf717e94cc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nino" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="uk-unique-taxpayer-reference-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10817">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10817">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10818">Уникальный справочный номер налогоплательщика</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10818">Unique Taxpayer Reference Number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10819">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10819">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10820">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10820">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10821">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10821">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10822">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10822">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10823">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10823">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10824">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10824">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10825">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10825">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10826">10 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10826">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
 
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10827">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10827">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10828">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10828">10 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10829">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10829">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10830">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10830">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10831">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10831">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10832">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10832">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10833">Функция находит  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10833">The function  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10834">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10834">A keyword from  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- U.K. Unique Taxpayer Reference Number -->
      <Entity id="ad4a8116-0db8-439a-b545-6d967642f0ec" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="us-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10854">Номер банковского счета в США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10854">U.S. bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10855">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10855">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10856">6–17 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10856">6-17 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10857">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10857">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10858">6–17 последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10858">6-17 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10859">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10859">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10860">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10860">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10861">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10861">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10862">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10862">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10863">регулярное выражение Regex_usa_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10863">The regular expression Regex_usa_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10864">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_usa_Bank_Account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10864">A keyword from Keyword_usa_Bank_Account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.S. Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="a2ce32a8-f935-4bb6-8e96-2a5157672e2c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_usa_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_usa_Bank_Account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="us-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10894">Номер водительского удостоверения для США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10894">U.S. driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10895">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10895">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10896">Зависит от штата.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10896">Depends on the state</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10897">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10897">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10898">зависит от состояния, например Нью-Йорк:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10898">depends on the state -- for example, New York:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10899">будут совпадать девять цифр в формате ddd ddd ddd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10899">nine digits formatted like ddd ddd ddd will match.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10900">девять цифр, например dddddd, не будут совпадать.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10900">nine digits like ddddddddd will not match.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10901">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10901">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10902">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10902">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10903">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10903">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10904">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10904">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10905">функция Func_new_york_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10905">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10906">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10906">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10907">обнаружено ключевое слово из списка Keyword_us_drivers_license.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10907">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10908">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10908">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10909">функция Func_new_york_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10909">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10910">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10910">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10911">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10911">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-10912">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_us_drivers_license не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-10912">No keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="dfeb356f-61cd-459e-bf0f-7c6d28b458c6 patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="us-individual-taxpayer-identification-number-itin"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11010">Идентификационный номер налогоплательщика (ITIN) для США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11010">U.S. individual taxpayer identification number (ITIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11011">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11011">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11012">девять цифр, которые начинаются с "9" и содержат "7" или "8" в качестве четвертой цифры, при желании отформатированные с пробелами или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11012">nine digits that start with a "9" and contain a "7" or "8" as the fourth digit, optionally formatted with spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11013">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11013">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11014">отформатированный:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11014">formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11015">цифра "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11015">the digit "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11016">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11016">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11017">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11017">a space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11018">"7" или "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11018">a "7" or "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11019">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11019">a digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11020">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11020">a space, or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11021">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11021">four digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11022">unformatted:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11022">unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11023">цифра "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11023">the digit "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11024">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11024">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11025">"7" или "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11025">a "7" or "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11026">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11026">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11027">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11027">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11028">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11028">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11029">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11029">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11030">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11030">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11031">Функция Func_formatted_itin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11031">The function Func_formatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11032">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_itin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11032">A keyword from Keyword_itin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11033">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11033">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11034">Функция Func_unformatted_itin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11034">The function Func_unformatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11035">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_itin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11035">A keyword from Keyword_itin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11036">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11036">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11037">Функция Func_formatted_itin или Func_unformatted_itin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11037">The function Func_formatted_itin or Func_unformatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.S. Individual Taxpayer Identification Number (ITIN) -->
    <Entity id="e55e2a32-f92d-4985-a35d-a0b269eb687b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_formatted_itin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_itin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_formatted_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_itin" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11038">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11038">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_itin"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11039">Keyword_itin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11039">Keyword_itin</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11040">налогоплательщик</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11040">taxpayer</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11041">tax id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11041">tax id</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11042">tax identification</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11042">tax identification</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11043">itin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11043">itin</span></span>

## <a name="us-social-security-number-ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11052">Номер социального обеспечения (SSN) для США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11052">U.S. social security number (SSN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11053">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11053">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11054">девять цифр, которые могут быть в форматированном или неформатированном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11054">nine digits, which may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

> [!NOTE]
> <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11055">Есть SSN выдан до середины 2011 г., он отличается строгим форматированием, при котором определенные части номера должны входить в указанные диапазоны (при этом нет контрольной суммы).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11055">If issued before mid-2011, an SSN has strong formatting where certain parts of the number must fall within certain ranges to be valid (but there's no checksum).</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11056">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11056">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11057">четыре функции искать SSNs в четырех различных шаблонах:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11057">four functions look for SSNs in four different patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11058">Func_ssn находит SSN со строгим форматированием с тире или пробелами, выданные до 2011 г. (ццц-цц-цццц ИЛИ ццц цц цццц);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11058">Func_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11059">Func_unformatted_ssn находит SSN со строгим форматированием, выданные до 2011 г. (без форматирования в виде девяти последовательных цифр — ццццццццц);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11059">Func_unformatted_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11060">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn находит SSN с тире или пробелами, выданные после 2011 г. (ццц-цц-цццц ИЛИ ццц цц цццц);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11060">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11061">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn находит SSN без форматирования в виде девяти последовательных цифр, выданные после 2011 г. (ццццццццц).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11061">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11062">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11062">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11063">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11063">No</span></span>


### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11064">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11064">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11065">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11065">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11066">Функция Func_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11066">The function Func_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11067">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11067">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11068">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11068">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11069">Функция Func_unformatted_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11069">The function Func_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11070">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11070">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11071">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11071">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11072">Функция Func_randomized_formatted_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11072">The function Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11073">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11073">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11074">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 55 % верно обнаружила этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в пределах ближайших 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11074">A DLP policy is 55% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11075">Функция Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11075">The function Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11076">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11076">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>


```xml
<!-- U.S. Social Security Number (SSN) -->
  <Entity id="a44669fe-0d48-453d-a9b1-2cc83f2cba77" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_formatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="55">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
  </Entity>
```

## <a name="us--uk-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11091">США и Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11091">U.S. / U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11092">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11092">passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11093">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11093">The U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11094">Объект типа конфиденциальной информации passport number доступен в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11094">passport number sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11095">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11095">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11096">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11096">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11097">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11097">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11098">девять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11098">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11099">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11099">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11100">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11100">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11101">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11101">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11102">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11102">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11103">функция Func_usa_uk_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11103">The function Func_usa_uk_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11104">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11104">A keyword from Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="178ec42a-18b4-47cc-85c7-d62c92fd67f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_usa_uk_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="ukraine-passport-domestic"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11125">Внутренний паспорт гражданина Украины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11125">Ukraine passport domestic</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11126">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11126">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11127">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11127">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11128">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11128">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11129">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11129">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11130">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11130">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11131">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11131">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11132">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11132">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11133">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11133">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11134">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11134">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11135">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11135">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11136">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11136">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11137">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11137">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11138">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11138">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11139">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11139">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11140">Regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11140">The regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11141">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11141">A keyword from Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic is found.</span></span>

```xml

      <Entity id="1817a540-221f-4459-9202-3bd78b81d803" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="ukraine-passport-international"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11150">Паспорт гражданина Украины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11150">Ukraine passport international</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11151">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11151">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11152">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11152">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11153">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11153">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11154">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11154">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11155">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11155">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11156">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11156">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11157">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11157">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11158">восьми-символьный буквонумерный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11158">eight-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11159">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11159">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11160">восьми-символьный буквонумерный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11160">eight-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11165">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11165">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11166">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11166">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11167">Regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11167">The regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8c0a2-11168">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c0a2-11168">A keyword from Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ukraine Passport International -->
      <Entity id="cfbe032d-22e0-4f28-ab68-d66e9641f1e2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
